{"data":{"page":{"id":"442a430c-5361-5948-a5d3-34ce367b4f83","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/proyecto2025/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived template without DB</a></p>\n<p>Proyecto2025 contacted us (Webmarket) to build a website to feature their real state properties and allow customers to search them. They also wanted a flexible system to edit, add or remove properties easily.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 101%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b078219f3586dca4319e109b3384e586/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b078219f3586dca4319e109b3384e586/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/b078219f3586dca4319e109b3384e586/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/b078219f3586dca4319e109b3384e586/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/b078219f3586dca4319e109b3384e586/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>At this point, I didn’t have a system or CMS with this sort of functionality. The open source options available at that time were also very insufficient for the requirements, so I decided to build my own bespoke solution. I called it INMOFlash, because it was based in Flash, PHP and MySQL.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8058bf6af20bdd919eefad4125232e42/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8058bf6af20bdd919eefad4125232e42/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/8058bf6af20bdd919eefad4125232e42/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/8058bf6af20bdd919eefad4125232e42/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/8058bf6af20bdd919eefad4125232e42/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>The combination of using Flash for the UI and MySQL and PHP for the backend was a winning solution in terms of creativity and UX. Years after, I realised that Flash was not the best option for SEO, therefore this solution didn’t have a very long future, but at the time, it was quite impressive and flexible.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 67.42596810933941%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/6b333/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/f3ce7/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/72342/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/6b333/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/b2533/3.jpg 1200w,\n/static/03b7f720dde47d7d32743abb552da1b3/6c9d1/3.jpg 1317w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.05649717514125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0f62e911024954c2a10a781522a9e012/6b333/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0f62e911024954c2a10a781522a9e012/f3ce7/4.jpg 200w,\n/static/0f62e911024954c2a10a781522a9e012/72342/4.jpg 400w,\n/static/0f62e911024954c2a10a781522a9e012/6b333/4.jpg 800w,\n/static/0f62e911024954c2a10a781522a9e012/11048/4.jpg 1062w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.12252591894439%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-imag